      <h3>
        <span class="comment-vote">
            <span id="c-967361974" class="vote-count">124</span>
              <a id="btn-967361974" href="" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="967361974">有用</a>

        </span>
        <span class="comment-info">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/nowstill/">𝛁</a>
            <span class="user-stars allstar20 rating" title="较差"></span>
          <a class="comment-time" href="/comment/967361974">2015-10-12 21:49:26</a>
          <span class="comment-location"></span>
        </span>
      </h3>
      <p class="comment-content">
      
        <span class="short">不接受这种莫名其妙的好评。从拖拖沓沓的环境描写开始到每个人都是王琦瑶，okay我假设是铺陈但后来关于弄堂谣言鸽子的意象又没回照到，而且根本没谁当得到王琦瑶。后半部分开始描写的人心也够诡谲，几段感情更加没头没尾，唯一还可以的部分留在苏州，送豆腐的阿二最动人。原本还期待这根线有发展。</span>
      </p>
        <div class="report-comment" data-url="https://book.douban.com/subject/1082349/?comment_id=967361974"></div>
    </div>
  </li>

